Pre-Game Insights: Netherlands striker Cody Gakpo expects more space for his team to attack in the upcoming match against Germany.
Germany leads the standings with seven points, two more than the second-placed Netherlands.
Virgil van Dijk will miss the match due to a one-match ban.
Ronald Koeman mentioned that either Stefan de Vrij or Denzel Dumfries will replace Van Dijk as captain.
